<title>PHILIPPINES: RESEARCH ALERT - BPI rated long-term buy.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - BPI rated long-term buy.</headline>
<dateline>MANILA 1996-10-09</dateline>
<text>
<p>Sun Hung Kai Securities recommended on Wednesday a long-term buy on Bank of the Philippine Islands following its merger with CityTrust Banking Corp.</p>
<p>&quot;While the merger of the two banks is expected to result in synergies of the two banks' strength in the consumer banking business, integration of operations may take a while to complete,&quot; Sun Hung Kai said in an advisory to clients.</p>
<p>&quot;To cite, the merger of Unionbank and Interbank in 1993/94 took around one year to fully consolidate the two banks' operations,&quot; it added.</p>
<p>The merger of the two banks took effect on Monday.</p>
<p>- Manila newsroom 63 2 841-8937 fax 8176267</p>
